Gradient descent algorithm¶

In [1]:
x = 2
lr = 0.0033
max_iter = 10000
iter = 0
precision = 0.000001
prev_step_size = 1
gf = lambda x:(x+3)**2
In [2]:
gd = []
while(precision<prev_step_size and iter<max_iter):
    prv = x
    x = x-lr*gf(prv)
    prev_step_size = abs(x-prv)
    iter += 1
    print("Iterations: ",iter,"Values: ",x)
    gd.append(x)
